## Featured project: TokenBridge

**A cross-border tokenized settlement platform** — applying the pattern behind Project Guardian (tokenized deposits + atomic delivery-versus-payment) to a demonstrable, end-to-end build.

![Architecture diagram](docs/architecture-diagram.png)

**What it demonstrates:**
- Atomic DvP settlement between two tokenized currencies, removing the principal risk window that correspondent banking carries
- Compliance enforced at the smart contract level via a permissioned allow-list — not just in application logic
- Full BA deliverable set alongside the code: BRD, process maps (as-is vs to-be), product backlog with named personas, sprint plan, and UAT test cases

**Stack:** Solidity, Hardhat, OpenZeppelin · Node.js/TypeScript, Express, PostgreSQL · React, wagmi · Polygon Amoy testnet

